    "documentation": "Easily create shareable dashboards that make key business data, metrics and KPIs clear and easy-to-understand.\n\n#### Authentication Ways\n\n-   API Key\n\n#### API Key\n\nPlease follow up the below steps to get your API Key\n\n1. Click on your initials in the top right hand corner.\n   ![Geckoboard API Key](https://geckoboard-2.intercom-attachments-1.com/i/o/479792051/601a615923c2f58e79a2b6d4/highlight_initials.png)\n2. From the dropdown, select Account.\n3. On the Account Details screen, scroll down and look for API Key towards the bottom of the page.\n   ![Geckoboard Account](https://geckoboard-2.intercom-attachments-1.com/i/o/479792052/03b1a299e768438656d56ec8/highlight_api_key.png)\n",
    "integration_id": "5f64aa12-af5b-497c-9b73-14cbad199381",
    "content": {
        "api_key": {
            "validate": {
                "url": "https://api.geckoboard.com",
                "method": "get",
                "headers": {
                    "Authorization": "Basic convertBufferBase64String({{secrets.api_key}}:)"
                },
                "response": {
                    "error": {
                        "code": "{{response.status}}",
                        "message": "{{response.data.errors[0].message}}"
                    },
                    "output": "{{response.data}}"
                }
            },
            "parameters": [
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "Api Key is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "Refer to the <a href='https://support.geckoboard.com/en/articles/6055693-find-your-geckoboard-api-key' target='blank'>Geckoboard authenticaton documentation</a> for detailed instructions on getting your api key.",
                        "displayName": "Api Key",
                        "displayType": "password",
                        "placeholder": "",
                        "dependencies": {
                            "conditions": [
                                {
                                    "field": "type",
                                    "value": "api_key",
                                    "operator": "EQUALS"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    },
                    "name": "api_key"
                }
            ]
        },
        "parameters": [
            {
                "meta": {
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "label": "Api Key",
                            "value": "api_key"
                        }
                    ],
                    "validation": {
                        "required": true,
                        "requiredDetail": {
                            "errorMsg": "Authentication Type is required"
                        }
                    },
                    "description": "Choose the type of authentication you want to use.",
                    "displayName": "Authentication Type",
                    "displayType": "select",
                    "placeholder": "Select an authentication type"
                },
                "name": "type"
            }
        ]
    },
